img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EM7UFW9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEM7UFW9.png&h=61d5696c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n影到沾有血跡既豬嘴"},{"pid":"08782c62ea28ef12a3e6f7cfad6013e64d4797a0","tid":1590383,"uid":74065,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:38:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QMAOLpD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQMAOLpD.png&h=5f0299a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n元朗721無差別恐怖襲擊事年<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uE79uRA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuE79uRA.png&h=7c280c1b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n甚至有孕婦係事件中受傷 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RXjDob1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRXjDob1.png&h=02251cd2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n訪問721傷者之一柳俊江 中途喊左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fdef9Ss.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffdef9Ss.png&h=6700cdc0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n一早報左警 警察回覆處理緊 但45分鐘過去完全無警察到場<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9S4ozjC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9S4ozjC.png&h=c2d4e86d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n警察終於到場 但白衣人已經走晒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9TAfqry.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9TAfqry.png&h=83f6727f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄉黑同黑警FD過夾BAND <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Z2UFZ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Z2UFZ8.png&h=e788ea72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李漢民安撫鄉黑 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jcvrw66.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJcvrw66.png&h=6fb19559&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n講述當晚一個白衣都無被捕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ak3piNr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fak3piNr.png&h=988960a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講述因721對警察信心已到零 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6RujR7S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6RujR7S.png&h=306b06ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n811太古站0距離開槍 暴打市民<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qx9uUR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qx9uUR.png&h=04069efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有少女中布袋彈致盲  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kgBqNGW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkgBqNGW.png&h=1ed1d35a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n黑警係醫院偷聽病人病情<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJp4iO3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJp4iO3.png&h=c42fef21&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n831太古站無差別毆打市民, 當中有3個傷者失蹤<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dz6Vquv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdz6Vquv.png&h=9f66d2fe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n公開左CCTV CAP圖 但見唔到事實既真相<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8zDogw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8zDogw.jpg&h=3cd8d212&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n721唔見人831打死人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bpz703Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBpz703Q.png&h=1bef4963&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nCCTVB有幸登上韓國媒體 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbtpiQP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsbtpiQP.png&h=1411247c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n員工被篤灰清算 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5k4WUpx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5k4WUpx.png&h=78ed32c2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n講述被捕人士係新屋嶺比人打至骨折虐待"},{"pid":"afc2273d15a9c83d9653d1463e7844aaab4e005e","tid":1590383,"uid":74065,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Ui43i7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Ui43i7.png&h=bed60d01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n原來特首係由1200人選